1. *Riječi* su najmoćniji alat u ljudskom rukovanju. (Words are the most powerful tool in human handling.)

2. Uvijek se sjećam njenih *riječi*. (I always remember her words.)

3. On se oprostio sa nama riječima hvale. (He said goodbye to us with words of praise.)

4. On se nadao da će njegove *riječi* imati neki utjecaj. (He hoped that his words would have some impact.)

5. Ona nije mogla vjerovati u njegove *riječi*. (She couldn't believe in his words.)

6. Ona je bila uvjerena da su njene *riječi* istinite. (She was convinced that her words were true.)